channel.title: ▒ExoticPK▒~200x exp rate~Join Today!~[RELEASED AS A SOURCE]
channel.description:
Hello People! I am now releasing ExoticPK ! I'm not that good at advertisements :\ but heres some features -
[b][u]Updates[/u][/b]
- added druidic ritual quest. ( help from Yong's EasyRSC tutorial)
- removed dueling
- 150x exp rate
-max stat is 125... max combat is 156!
- Clan raid mini-game
- commands are ::edge ::stuck ::varrock ::castle ::caltar ::valtar ::say :: onlinelist :: online :: pkbox ::fatigue ::greaters
- Fully working shops
- fully working masterfisher
Here are some pics of the mini-game Clan Raid [IMG]http://i669.photobucket.com/albums/vv54/2_dads/kbd.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i669.photobucket.com/albums/vv54/2_dads/clanraid.jpg[/img]
Heres a pic of the pkbox [IMG]http://img207.imageshack.us/img207/3296/pkbox.png[/img]
To find more updates check forums! Hope u try my server out. Client download and forums link is in my signature.
[credits]70% credit to me 5% credit to pork pl0x 10% credit to xEnt for the EasyRSC source 10% credit to Yong Min and 5% credit to people that wanted my server up and to people who helped me when I asked a question.
King Regards, Bladex0x.
